                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070916-104-off552 t18070916-104-crimeloc554"></join> on the 11th of September, I went out about twelve, I left the tools in the house. I missed my saws, and stock, and bit.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you ever find your tools. - A. No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18070916-104-person928">
                  CHRISTOPHER 
                  FISH
               <interp inst="t18070916-104-person928" type="surname" value="FISH"></interp>
